	<element name="Volume of Discipline" type="Sub Race" source="Sionnach's Mind" id="ID_SUB_RACE_VOLUMEOFDISCIPLINE">
		<supports>Scriptorii</supports>
		<requirements />
		<description>
		<p>Your core text is a book of mastering the body through the mind, endowing you with great control over your physical form.</p>
		<p>
			<span class="feature">Ability Score Increase.</span> Your Dexterity score increases by 1.<br />
			<span class="feature">Proficiencies.</span> You have proficiency in your choice of the Sleight of Hand or Stealth skill. You are also proficient with two martial weapons of your choice.<br />
			<span class="feature">Martial Insight.</span> Your understanding of the body makes you a deadly foe. When you make a weapon attack, you can give yourself a bonus to the attack and damage roll equal to your Intelligence modifier. After you do so, you can’t use this trait again until you finish a short or long rest.
		</p>
		</description>
